The following are the rules of the District Level Control Committee: -
(1) To regulate the National Mission on Natural Farming at the district level.
(2) To make available information related to natural farming to the state level natural farming cell.
(d) Taluk Level Control Committee
Functions of the Taluk Level Control Committee: -
(1) To make available information on natural farming to the District Level Control Committee.
